==Hindi==

===Etymology===
From Sanskrit वस्तु

===Noun===
'''वस्तु''' (vastu) {{m}}

# a [[thing]]
# [[stuff]]
# [[baggage]]
# [[material]]
# something real or existent
# a [[commodity]]
# essential [[property]], [[nature]], [[essence]], [[substance]]
# the [[object]] (of); the pith or substance (of)

====Urdu spelling====
*{{URchar|[[وستو]]}}

===Synonyms===
*[[चीज़]]

