==Sanskrit==

===Noun===
'''वस्तु''' (vastu) {{n}}

# a [[thing]]
# any really existing or abiding substance or essence, thing, object, article
# [[seat]], [[place]]
# [[matter]], [[circumstance]]
# [[substance]], contents or subject (of a poem etc.)

===Noun===
'''वस्तु''' (vastu) {{f}}

# [[brightening]], [[dawning]]

